        <li><strong>ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE and INTERNET:</strong> Used to check network connectivity and load content like advertisements.</li>
        <li><strong>READ_PHONE_STATE:</strong> Used to access device state for functional purposes without storing or sharing any contact data.</li>
    </ul>

